API Gateway (NestJS) - Handles requests and forwards them to microservices.
User Service (NestJS, separate server) - Manages users, profiles, and authentication.
Admin Service (NestJS, separate server) - Handles admin-related operations.
Order Service (NestJS, separate server) - Manages orders, payments, and shipping.
Product Service (NestJS, separate server) - Handles products, categories, and inventory.
Database (PostgreSQL/MySQL) - A single database can be shared across microservices or separate DBs per service.
Message Broker (RabbitMQ/Kafka/NATS) - Enables communication between services.